section.def:
licence
                (許可證) means a licence issued under these
            regulations;

paragraph.content:
present the licence to the owner of the vessel, aircraft or vehicle in or
                    on which the reserved commodity was imported (conveyance
                    owner);

subparagraph.content:
deliver the licence to the Director, or (if applicable) inform the
                        Director, using the specified system, of the licence number of the licence;
                        and

paragraph.content:
present the licence to the owner of the vessel, aircraft or vehicle in or
                    on which the reserved commodity is intended to be exported (conveyance
                            owner);

deliver the licence to the Director, or (if applicable) inform the
                    Director, using the specified system, of the licence number of the licence;
                    and
